Best known for his roles in Titanic and HBO’s, Big Love, Bill Paxton has died today due to surgery complications at the age of 61. Paxton was an Emmy Award- winning actor who began acting in 1970. Awww man, not Radio Raheem! Veteran actor Bill Nunn, most famous for playing Radio Raheem in Spike Lee’s Oscar-nominated film “Do The Right Thing,” has died.
